DialogueNode.dialogue: The new HR hire, right? Nice to meet you! I'm Dave.
It's nice to meet you too, Dave! What do you do around here?
Ah, I handle the tech and stuff. You know how it goes. Always on the move.
Ah yes of course. I get you. What's your experience been like at the company?
Yeah, I understand. You must have a lot to take care of.
Great! I love it here. Going on 10 years. Best job I've ever had.
Of course! But it's fun. Always getting to figure out new things, even after a decade.
Yup! Came here fresh out of school. I'm sure you'll do great here too.
Thanks Dave! I hope so too.
I'll see you around! Don't be a stranger!
